data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET!!! Opportunity knocking, This spacious 3/2 home with a pool overlooking canal views will take your breath away. Tiled throughout. Owner made some updates to the home. Close to Hard Rock Stadium! East Miramar with no association, centrally located close to shopping centers, highways and great schools. Brand new roof installed in 2023. Impact windows throughout the home installed in 2022. Garage converted into an In-law quarters for added income.
